headline: Friday's big stock stories: What’s likely to move the market in the next trading session
summary: Stocks fell on Thursday after a volatile session that saw a more than 1,000-point reversal on the Dow and a more than 2% drop in the Nasdaq.

headline: RTX's Collins Aerospace and the Royal Netherlands Air and Space Force establish new military avionics service center
summary: Collins Aerospace, an RTX (NYSE: RTX) business, and the Royal Netherlands Air and Space Force (RNLASF) have signed a contract to build a new military avionics service center in the Netherlands to support European F-35 and CH-47F fleets.
